---
title: Chinese Garlic Beef & Snow Pea Stir-Fry with Crushed Peanuts
description: If you’re a long-time lover of the signature mix of sweet, spicy and salty, then you're going to go nuts for this stir-fry. Combine lightly marinated beef with courgette, carrot and crisp snow peas for an array of flavours and textures.
